{"title": "How to make a \u2018gentleman\u2019s agreement\u2019 work for you", "tags": "business", "timestamp": "2023-03-25", "content": "A \u201cgentleman\u2019s agreement\u201d is one of those feel-good traditions we like to hold dear, but it is worth remembering that such deals do not hold water.\nVerbal arrangements between two parties are by nature informal and usually based on trust; there is nothing binding on anyone."}